def_cn: (婉指女性或男性性别特征明显)天赋异禀的，硕大的
def_en: If someone says that a woman is well-endowed, they mean that she has large breasts. If someone says that a man is well-endowed, they mean that he has a large penis. People often use this expression if they are trying to be polite.
A well-endowed organization has a lot of money or resources.
